Advanced Locomotion System v4


Kung Fu PK-MAN is a Kung Fu character, serving as the main character in the game, featuring four styles of totem designs - Chinese, Japanese, American, and Punk.


The KFP character “BasicPack" is equipped with a basic weapon "double batons". The character possesses muscle deformation and 52 basic facial expression deformations. A straightforward character blueprint controls the character components and material properties like bloodstains, dirt marks, watermarks, and other material options.


Included is a tutorial demonstration on integrating the KFP character blueprint into the ALSv4 advanced character movement system, with adaptability to other motion systems following the tutorial's instructions.


the character offers 12 facial war paint options.


The highly adjustable material sphere allows for modifications to nearly 90% of parameters in material management, covering style totems, dust, bloodstains, oil marks, watermarks, freckles, bloodshot eyes, lip colors, and smoky eye prints. Clothing and various props are equipped with color IDs.
